    "body": "You should already be able to do this by adding a WithSpriteBody or WithFacingSpriteBody on every unit in the map and have a condition on it that is activated through LUA when you pick up the flag.\r\n\r\nAdding support for it through traits would be best left to a mod as that is not a good use of the already limited developer time on this project, also it is pretty niche and if it can already be done through LUA there is not enough of an incentive to spend time on it."
